    dc:description "Figs 33–40. Dichagyris spp. 33–35 =D. furiosa kugitanga ssp. n., Turkmenistan, Kugitang Tau: 33 = holotype, male; 34–35 = paratype, males. 36–38 = D. contermina (Corti, 1929): 36 = holotype of Dichagyris wolfi Hacker, 1986, male, Turkey, Prov. Mardin; 37 = male, Turkey, Prov. Urfa, Halfeti; 38 = female, Turkey, Prov. Urfa, Halfeti. 39–40 = Dichagyris contermina melanographa ssp. n., Iran, Zagros Mts, Kasri-Shirin: 39 = holotype, male; 40 = paratype, female" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10272223/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10272245>
